Cell["\<\
As for the density function, we use known result for the Sun (aka, the Sun \
model). The density is exponential function with given factor and known \
magnitude factor.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9713909896155243`*^9, 
  3.9713910605932503`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"193da6e5-4d38-9f40-be63-\
b663a42d8964"],

