Cell["\<\
The \\(W\\) matrix, as was mentioned above, is constructed from mixing \
angles. The formula is given below. We use values for the angles from the \
work [Casas et al, 2016].\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9713910801151237`*^9, 
  3.971391143837702*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a8d59cf2-0fc7-0249-b57a-\
47d7279e9daa"],

