1da4d3319506"],

Cell["\<\
According to work [Casas et al], the more \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]correct\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] result would be obtained if one uses the \
Dorman-Prince method of Runge--Kutta family. Mathematica allows to explicitly \
set coefficients for Runge--Kutta method used internally.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.971391165240814*^9, 
  3.9713912582349625`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"84450f4a-6f8a-cf48-8960-\
634c6fd95b19"],

